            "label": "Deploy RethinkDB Native Cluster HA node",
            "command": "set -euo pipefail\nlog() { printf '[rethinkdb_native_cluster_ha] %s\\n' \"$*\"; }\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/rethinkdb_native_cluster_ha/compose.yml pull\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/rethinkdb_native_cluster_ha/compose.yml up -d\ndocker compose -f /opt/octastack/rethinkdb_native_cluster_ha/compose.yml ps\n      log \"node deployment complete\"\n",
            "sudo": true
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "node_step_4",
          "type": "configCommandNode",
          "position": {
            "x": 885,
            "y": 4815
          },
          "data": {
            "label": "Document RethinkDB Native Cluster HA topology",
            "command": "set -euo pipefail\ncat >/tmp/rethinkdb_native_cluster_ha-topology.md <<'EOF'\n# RethinkDB Native Cluster HA\n\nMembers:\n- rethinkdb-01: 10.0.19.11 (rethinkdb)\n- rethinkdb-02: 10.0.19.12 (rethinkdb)\n- rethinkdb-03: 10.0.19.13 (rethinkdb)\n\nThree RethinkDB members form a native cluster; non-primary members join the generated first member.\nEOF\ncat /tmp/rethinkdb_native_cluster_ha-topology.md\n",
            "sudo": true
          }
        },
